HEADWORD: Trinoctial
<hw>Tri*noc"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>trinoctialis</ets> for three nights; <ets>tri-</ets> (see
<er>Tri-</er>) + <ets>nox</ets>, <ets>noctis</ets>, night.]</ety>
